cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and dialog systems. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a neural network model for the task-oriented dialog system. Additionally, it may belong to cs.SD (Software Engineering) as it involves the development of a software system for dialog management. Finally, it may belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for modeling the dialog system.
